1.) Create following subdirectories:
mkdir build
mkdir logs
mkdir streams [OPTIONAL]

2.)copy desired streams to the created streams/ folder [OPTIONAL]

3.)cd build

4.)To configure the project, simply type
      cmake ..

5.)To build the project, proceed with
      make

**Further explanation: it has been assumed that the TS packet length is of
188 bytes, according to ISO-13818-1, for the sync error calculation